{"tid":1728913,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[對外文宣分析] 天橋橫額 有咩問政府系列","createTime":"2019-11-17T05:13:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T09:25:05.000Z","uid":44925,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"86ee3552366b514b71f6c6902a720d4c82fc5ba7","tid":1728913,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T05:13:03.000Z","msg":"抗爭冇對外信息，冇話俾人地知你做緊乜，係致敗要點。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/exjeCS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/exjeCS</a><br />\n<br />\n睇左呢個post 樓主講得岩 我地<span style=\"color: gold;\">對外信息同行動開始不成比例</span><br />\n可能你會問 民意歸哂邊 仲文宣黎做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n答: 大家既諗法係岩 我自己都唔係民意撚 我一直認為<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">若果民意唔能夠轉化為行動</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">民意係無用</span></span><br />\n<br />\n咁仲要對外信息做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n答:係俾藍屍同港豬睇 <br />\n無錯 民意已定型 我地係無可能再爭取任何民意 但係我地可以令到佢地<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">懷疑人生</span></span> <br />\n咁即係點?<br />\n諗下對家用咩招黎對付我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢無可能令黃既民意轉藍 但係佢可以分化我地<br />\n佢令深黃同淺黃間互相不信任 佢令勇武和理非製造矛盾 從而令我地內部瓦解<br />\n我地其實應該用返相同招數  我地無可能令藍屍港豬轉黃 <span style=\"color: blue;\">但我地要令佢地自己分裂 質疑政府 質疑警察</span><br />\n<br />\n點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n答:  路障手足其實唔駛同班司機拗<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1719797\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1719797</a><br />\n<br />\n正如我呢個post好多人所認同既一點 將<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">所有野</span></span><br />\n話之你堵路私了裝修定咩都好 全部<span style=\"color: red;\">拋個波俾政府</span><br />\n至於具體行動方面 其實我地好耐無做一樣野: <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">天橋橫額</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qB4WMbS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqB4WMbS.jpg&h=7bddd6c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uzZDe5c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuzZDe5c.jpg&h=060846a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我建議: 既然我地有紅隧優勢 我地就好應該利用紅隧天橋 其他各大天橋 掛橫額拋波俾政府<br />\n唔駛多字 簡單幾個字就可<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有咩問政府</span></span> <br />\n或者 有咩問警察 有咩問建制 有咩問TVB<br />\n<br />\n重點係 殺人放火都好 拋波俾政府 呢個係我地既永遠對外信息<br />\n<br />\n有個前提 我地一定要守住紅隧 全世界入POLY!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8002b71bc9eb55f8de2c1c0294fe9297e0cddca2","tid":1728913,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T05:13:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有咩問政府</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"f5dc09ba4dfae22ebe6212ac5374ab9992a2b6f7","tid":1728913,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T05:15:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有咩問警察</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"d30ab3122f326ce6ce71918d0e9109af8c6c9c2f","tid":1728913,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T05:17:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>有咩問建制</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"f5cdc0a5d3b569fca24317f36a39b42398c659e8","tid":1728913,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T05:18:18.000Z","msg":"如果大家有其他建議 都可以一齊提出<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eae6305ce240348556cc080362aa58c5a85e057d","tid":1728913,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T05:19:48.000Z","msg":"不過首要任務係救左Poly先"},{"pid":"d192a2891833859676628562ef994de15e63d528","tid":1728913,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T05:58:22.000Z","msg":"救Poly!"},{"pid":"92d8d3b78c6488cf3d8e1da503b08abe87eb41e7","tid":1728913,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T05:58:52.000Z","msg":"救Poly"},{"pid":"ef8f5e4ebebd097e90182447edcd5b800227cd84","tid":1728913,"uid":251414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T08:02:30.000Z","msg":"ccccccccccccccc"},{"pid":"f676f5b82d5364192d57ae75cc934238f30c40bb","tid":1728913,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef8f5e4ebebd097e90182447edcd5b800227cd84","tid":1728913,"uid":251414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T08:02:30.000Z","msg":"ccccccccccccccc"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T09:25:05.000Z","msg":"救POLY!"}]}